#  Kairoseed System v0.2

A closed-loop decision evolution system combining:
- Hypothesis generation (Kairoseed)
- Weighted evaluation (GSBS)
- Evolutionary refinement (PEE)
- Optional safety gating (AGT)
- Memory-driven learning

---

##  System Overview

Kairoseed is not a model.

It is a **structured decision evolution engine**.

It operates in a continuous loop:
INPUT → HYPOTHESES → GSBS → PEE → SELECTION → (AGT) → EXECUTION → MEMORY → LOOP

